{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":442,"text":"Twelve years ago, I was in the street writing my name"},{"time":4342,"text":"to say, \"I exist.\""},{"time":6181,"text":"Then I went to taking photos of people to paste them on the street"},{"time":11174,"text":"to say, \"They exist.\""},{"time":13531,"text":"From the suburbs of Paris to the wall of Israel and Palestine,"},{"time":18046,"text":"the rooftops of Kenya"},{"time":20456,"text":"to the favelas of Rio,"},{"time":22344,"text":"paper and glue -- as easy as that."}]},{"cues":[{"time":26087,"text":"I asked a question last year:"},{"time":28306,"text":"Can art change the world?"},{"time":30581,"text":"Well let me tell you,"},{"time":32583,"text":"in terms of changing the world there has been a lot of competition this year,"},{"time":36323,"text":"because the Arab Spring is still spreading,"},{"time":39517,"text":"the Eurozone has collapsed ... what else?"},{"time":42827,"text":"The Occupy movement found a voice,"},{"time":45820,"text":"and I still have to speak English constantly."},{"time":48292,"text":"So there has been a lot of change."}]},{"cues":[{"time":51125,"text":"So when I had my TED wish last year,"},{"time":53260,"text":"I said, look, I'm going to switch my concept."},{"time":56423,"text":"You are going to take the photos."},{"time":59091,"text":"You're going to send them to me."},{"time":61671,"text":"I'm going to print them and send them back to you."},{"time":64888,"text":"Then you're going to paste them where it makes sense"},{"time":67385,"text":"for you to place your own statement."}]},{"cues":[{"time":69260,"text":"This is Inside Out."},{"time":71729,"text":"One hundred thousand posters have been printed this year."},{"time":75912,"text":"Those are the kind of posters, let me show you."},{"time":79912,"text":"And we keep sending more every day."},{"time":82167,"text":"This is the size."},{"time":83611,"text":"Just a regular piece of paper with a little bit of ink on it."},{"time":87533,"text":"This one was from Haiti."}]},{"cues":[{"time":91048,"text":"When I launched my wish last year,"},{"time":93500,"text":"hundreds of people stood up and said they wanted to help us."},{"time":97925,"text":"But I say it has to be"},{"time":100142,"text":"under the conditions I've always worked:"},{"time":103596,"text":"no credit, no logos, no sponsoring."},{"time":107858,"text":"A week later, a handful of people were there ready to rock"},{"time":112208,"text":"and empower the people on the ground"},{"time":114662,"text":"who wanted to change the world."},{"time":116208,"text":"These are the people I want to talk about to you today."}]},{"cues":[{"time":121020,"text":"Two weeks after my speech, in Tunisia,"},{"time":126794,"text":"hundreds of portraits were made."},{"time":130545,"text":"And they pasted [over] every single portrait of the dictator"},{"time":134792,"text":"[with] their own photos."},{"time":136292,"text":"Boom! This is what happened."},{"time":139125,"text":"Slim and his friends went through the country"},{"time":140875,"text":"and pasted hundreds of photos everywhere"},{"time":143250,"text":"to show the diversity in the country."},{"time":146413,"text":"They really make Inside Out their own project."},{"time":150496,"text":"Actually, that photo was pasted in a police station,"},{"time":154042,"text":"and what you see on the ground"},{"time":155546,"text":"are ID cards of all the photos of people being tracked by the police."}]},{"cues":[{"time":161707,"text":"Russia. Chad wanted to fight against homophobia in Russia."},{"time":166417,"text":"He went with his friends in front of every Russian embassy in Europe"},{"time":170940,"text":"and stood there with the photos"},{"time":173000,"text":"to say, \"We have rights.\""},{"time":174760,"text":"They used Inside Out as a platform for protest."}]},{"cues":[{"time":179291,"text":"Karachi, Pakistan."},{"time":181208,"text":"Sharmeen is actually here."},{"time":183008,"text":"She organized a TEDx action out there"},{"time":186373,"text":"and made all the unseen faces of the city"},{"time":189404,"text":"on the walls in her town."},{"time":191667,"text":"And I want to thank her today."}]},{"cues":[{"time":193998,"text":"North Dakota. Standing Rock Nation,"},{"time":197773,"text":"in this Turtle Island, [unclear name] from the Dakota Lakota tribe"},{"time":203508,"text":"wanted to show that the Native Americans are still here."},{"time":206865,"text":"The seventh generation are still fighting for their rights."},{"time":210500,"text":"He pasted up portraits all over his reservation."},{"time":213475,"text":"And he's here also today."},{"time":215342,"text":"Each time I get a wall in New York,"},{"time":218842,"text":"I use his photos to continue spreading the project."}]},{"cues":[{"time":223863,"text":"Juarez: You've heard of the border --"},{"time":226917,"text":"one of the most dangerous borders in the world."},{"time":229750,"text":"Monica has taken thousands of portraits with a group of photographers"},{"time":234523,"text":"and covered the entire border."},{"time":237308,"text":"Do you know what it takes to do this?"},{"time":239333,"text":"People, energy, make the glue, organize the team."},{"time":243435,"text":"It was amazing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":245554,"text":"While in Iran at the same time"},{"time":248354,"text":"Abololo -- of course a nickname --"},{"time":250717,"text":"has pasted one single face of a woman"},{"time":253662,"text":"to show his resistance against the government."},{"time":257261,"text":"I don't have to explain to you what kind of risk he took for that action."}]},{"cues":[{"time":261971,"text":"There are tons of school projects."},{"time":264573,"text":"Twenty percent of the posters we are receiving comes from schools."},{"time":268223,"text":"Education is so essential."},{"time":270123,"text":"Kids just make photos in a class, the teacher receives them,"},{"time":273458,"text":"they paste them on the school."},{"time":275133,"text":"Here they even got the help of the firemen."},{"time":277125,"text":"There should be even more schools doing this kind of project."}]},{"cues":[{"time":280900,"text":"Of course we wanted to go back to Israel and Palestine."},{"time":286735,"text":"So we went there with a truck. This is a photobooth truck."},{"time":289770,"text":"You go on the back of that truck, it takes your photo,"},{"time":291981,"text":"30 seconds later take it from the side, you're ready to rock."},{"time":296104,"text":"Thousands of people use them"},{"time":299066,"text":"and each of them signs up for a two-state peace solution"},{"time":303237,"text":"and then walk in the street."},{"time":305167,"text":"This is march, the 450,000 march -- beginning of September."},{"time":309244,"text":"They were all holding their photo as a statement."},{"time":311554,"text":"On the other side, people were wrapping up streets, buildings."},{"time":315583,"text":"It's everywhere."},{"time":317085,"text":"Come on, don't tell me that people aren't ready for peace out there."}]},{"cues":[{"time":320104,"text":"These projects took thousands of actions in one year,"},{"time":324792,"text":"making hundreds of thousands of people participating,"},{"time":327958,"text":"creating millions of views."},{"time":331633,"text":"This is the biggest global art participatory project that's going on."}]},{"cues":[{"time":338738,"text":"So back to the question, \"Can art change the world?\""},{"time":342600,"text":"Maybe not in one year. That's the beginning."},{"time":346456,"text":"But maybe we should change the question."},{"time":349186,"text":"Can art change people's lives?"},{"time":351725,"text":"From what I've seen this year, yes."},{"time":355600,"text":"And you know what? It's just the beginning."},{"time":358283,"text":"Let's turn the world inside out together."},{"time":361071,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":362464,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}